ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 上面無睇唔緊要  最後有兩個POST 希望你可以知道  </span>  </span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我每日打開蘋果動新聞就係想睇下有幾多人跳樓燒炭死 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/271152/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/271152/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n睇到呢個POST 真係令人有種感覺  宜家嘅香港到底變成點  其實係連登都周不時有D POST 話自己對呢個世界絕望 想放棄啦 連登比較多嘅都係學生  咩事都好 千奇唔好尋死<br />\n 人人都會有煩惱 學業問題嘅 最多咪唔讀   其他問他嘅搵身邊嘅朋友傾下  之前聽過句話叫 <span style=\"color: red;\"> 關關難過關關過 </span>  呢句話我覺得好有用 希望可以鼓勵下有煩惱嘅各巴絲<br />\n(我記得之前有個巴打係留TG 話有人想尋死嘅話去搵佢傾下計先 但我搵唔番啦)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  ［突發］金鐘麥記開始多人    </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/231691/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/231691/page/1?ref=web</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">  連登仔第一次聚會  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span>  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/022451_194f5c6582bd1afcabbb1d267824c49d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F022451_194f5c6582bd1afcabbb1d267824c49d.jpg&h=e6c77804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖有排LOOP <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d37b25e55e90ee8acded889b50e8b4d4920d14","tid":514662,"uid":14447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T18:47:56.000Z","msg":"幾有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"